Description:
Smart, Spacious And Secure
Enjoy the style, security and low maintenance living of a modern townhouse with the space and feel of a family home. With an array of close by amenities; Hemmings Park, Greaves Reserve, Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School, Dandenong Market and Plaza, Dandenong Train Station, bus transportation and Eastlink, you’ll be set for life!
Boasting a floor plan of 19 squares, you begin with an open plan kitchen, dining and living room, perfect for both casual family living and entertaining friends. The generous kitchen features a timeless colour palette with stainless steel appliances, plenty of cupboard storage and a handy walk in pantry.
Also on offer are three spacious bedrooms with built in robes, a bathroom on each level plus separate WC. Further highlights of the home include tiled flooring, high ceilings, ducted heating, 2 x reverse cycle air conditioners, solar hot water system and downlights throughout.
Complimented by a secure, low maintenance rear courtyard, water tank, storage shed and double garage with remote access, this home is ready for new owners or tenants alike.
• Brand new, stylish townhouse with the feel of a family home
• Open plan kitchen, meals and living area, three bedrooms with built in robes, two bathrooms and a separate WC
• Ducted heating, 2 x reverse cycle air conditioners, high ceilings, solar hot water and downlights throughout
• Low maintenance courtyard, water tank, storage shed and double garage with remote access
• Located only minutes from the parks, schools, Dandenong Market and Plaza, Dandenong Train Station and Eastlink

Description:
Young, modern tri-level townhouse - 2 bathrooms!
Escape the ordinary with this near new, tri-level townhouse situated in the heart of Dandenong. Unique in design and offering a low maintenance life style making it perfectly suited to the owner-occupier or smart investor. 3 levels of quality, ground floor comprises garage with internal entry, spacious kitchen with adjoining meals/ living area, laundry, powder room and private courtyard with water tank. Second floor features master bedroom with robes and ensuite, large living area and balcony. Third floor boasts elegant A frame' ceilings, large open study/ living area, generous bedroom with robes and ensuite. With a fully functional floorplan and all of the benefits of being located within walking distance to Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, train station, buses and schools, this townhouse is the epitome of convenience. Move in immediately or lease immediately with income upon settlement.

Convenience & Central Position

Immersing its residents with unbeatable convenience coupled with low maintenance lifestyle appeal, this sleekly styled young apartment offers an outstanding opportunity for first-home buyers or savvy investors seeking to gain a foothold in the market or add to their portfolio.
Peacefully located on the first floor corner in a boutique apartment complex, this stunning residence adopts a sensational indoor-outdoor approach to lifestyle living. With a modern L shaped kitchen with island bench, living and dining zone incorporating stylish floorboards, tiled splashbacks, stainless steel appliances, feeding onto a private balcony accessible from both the living room and master bedroom. Each of the two bedrooms benefit from built-in-robes and are serviced by a central bathroom with toilet. Split system heating/air conditioning, intercom/passcode security entry plus secure parking complete this superb lifestyle package.

NEARLY NEW TOWNHOUSE
As you enter the property you will be greeted by large open plan living, meals and kitchen area. In addition to that there is a spacious ground floor bathroom, laundry and storage under stairs. On the top floor you will find 2 generously sized bedrooms with build in robes and another bathroom with separate toilet. With additional features that includes timber flooring throughout, gas ducted heating, two air conditioners (ground floor and top floor), gas appliances, dish washer. Outside is quite large back yard with a nice decking for enjoyment during sunny days and single lock up garage. There are just 2 unit on the block and there is no need for Body corporate. It’s a very quite location and close to Central Dandenong, Market, Schools, Hospital, Swimming Pool, Freeway entrance and Recreational facilities. Inspection will impress.

Description:
Your future is here.
Sale By SET DATE: Tuesday 31st July at 5pm (unless sold prior)
Don’t worry about maintenance, it’s all been done and to the highest standard.
This unique and enchanting home surrounded by quality properties is certainly an eye pleaser and ideal for those who love a flat home with little or no steps. Set on a spacious 529m2 (approx) block close to all the facilities that the City of Dandenong has to offer with its generous parks and walking tracks, shopping centres and schools.
Consisting of 3 large bedrooms plus multiple living areas, this home has everything you’d need and more! The main is particularly substantial with a plethora of robes and lovely ensuite. All bedrooms come with fans.
The living areas, one with a gas coal fireplace and bay windows provide a variety of functions. The near new kitchen has almost new appliances, stone benchtops and is extremely functional, leading to a meals area and a more formal dining space.
Outside is just as appealing. The undercover area off the kitchen provides more opportunity to enjoy the easily maintained and private garden. The double garage will lure all those handymen out there with its spaciousness and drive through access. Having the ability to access the garage undercover is another useful extra in a home that’s already full of wonderful surprises!
With security, including an alarm system, wall furnaces, quality blinds and carpets this is certainly a home of high appeal and one that seldom appears on the market. Situated in a quiet and ideal location, be quick as properties of this standard and quality won’t last.

Description:
Sold at Auction By Team Raghu for $440,000!
First home buyers, downsizers and investors will delight in this five year young, modern townhouse that combines street frontage with interior space and style. Leave behind the maintenance of your old property to simply move in, unpack and relax.
The light filled townhouse welcomes you with glossy floating floors and high ceilings. The ground floor open plan kitchen, meals and living area is accompanied by a laundry and powder room whilst upstairs accommodates two good sized bedrooms with built in robes, a study nook, central bathroom and second separate WC. Completing this homely package is a secure rear yard with a low maintenance garden to provide private outdoor space as well as a water tank, handy storage shed and large single garage.
Everyday living will also be a breeze with this great location; walk to Dandenong CBD, markets and shopping plaza, stroll to Hemmings Park or Greaves Reserve, Dandenong West Primary School and Dandenong High School. Convenient transport options are also available with nearby bus services, Dandenong Train Station, Eastlink, Princes Highway and the Dandenong Bypass.
• Five year young, two bedroom townhouse with street frontage
• Open plan kitchen, meals and living area, two bedrooms, study nook, bathroom and 2 x WC
• Private courtyard with low maintenance garden, water tank, storage shed and large single garage
• 3 x reverse cycle air conditioners, high ceilings, floating floors and NBN
• Close to schools, shops, markets, parks, train station and easy access to Eastlink and the Dandenong Bypass
